data.title: Watch Vera (2011) TV Series Free Online
data.meta_description: Watch Vera (2011) free starring Brenda Blethyn, Jon Morrison, Riley Jones and directed by Paul Whittington.
data.text: The central character is Detective Chief Inspector Vera Stanhope, who is obsessive about her work and driven by her own demons. If she's lonely she doesn't show it; she faces the world with caustic wit, guile, and courage. Her trusted, long-suffering colleague is Sergeant Joe Ashworth. Together they approach every new case with unparalleled gusto and professionalism.
